START
    LDA NUM1
    ADD NUM2
    STA TEMP

    LDX INDEX_VAL
    STX COUNT

    LDA TEMP
    MUL FACTOR
    SUB NUM3
    ADD BONUS
    STA RESULT

    LDA RESULT
    DIV FACTOR
    STA FINAL

NUM1      WORD 20
NUM2      WORD 10
NUM3      WORD 5
FACTOR    WORD 5
BONUS     WORD 8
INDEX_VAL WORD 2
COUNT     WORD 0
TEMP      WORD 0
RESULT    WORD 0
FINAL     WORD 0
END